{"tid":1721353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》】","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T22:41:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"bfdf17f528d0d893462d5ed0cfe450e257522f8a","tid":1721353,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"剛剛習近平在金磚國家領導人會晤上，提出「止暴制亂是香港當前最緊迫的任務」、恐嚇香港人之際，同一時間，美國國會再度出手。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉Mitch McConnell剛剛將《法案》提交參議院審議，並啟動「熱線」（hotline）機制。<br />\n<br />\n在「熱線」機制下，《法案》提交後六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前），沒有參議員反對的話，就當作參議院一致通過，法案就會明早交到白宮處理。<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n🗺【支持眾志國際連結眾籌】<br />\n讓香港人權民主法案遍地開花｜<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=ac19ab25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a>"},{"pid":"4e6f91e777c186ff37b4d98e27b88e4597aa2a9e","tid":1721353,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a0de838001d93fe148ae080f46658cf851980a","tid":1721353,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13faa1c258881dd621ce6faaed25b73477fa87c7","tid":1721353,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"推佢老母！！"},{"pid":"2cd36628e8e8c3e67c8891e37a934de8841b45a3","tid":17213